# ATK Management System

Next.js App Router + PostgreSQL + Prisma + NextAuth + shadcn/ui.

## Domain & route

| Modul | UI | API | Tabel DB |
|-------|-----|-----|----------|
| Platform | `/platform/*` (dashboard admin: `/platform/dashboard`) | `/api/platform/*` | `user` |
| Purchasing admin | `/purchasing/admin/*` | `/api/purchasing/*` | `atk_*` |
| Purchasing user | `/purchasing/user/*` | `/api/purchasing/*` | `atk_*` |
| IT staff | `/it/staff/*` | `/api/it/*` | `it_*` |
| IT user | `/it/user/*` | `/api/it/*` | `it_*` |

Permission: `lib/auth/permissions.ts`. Arsitektur: `docs/architecture.md`.

## Layout halaman

Ikuti `.cursor/rules/dashboard-pages.mdc` untuk shell, `PageActions`, filter horizontal, tabel tanpa Card, dan judul hanya di header.

## Konvensi umum

- UI teks Bahasa Indonesia; kode/identifier English.
- Minimalkan scope diff; ikuti pola file terdekat.
- **Jangan** impor `lib/db/prisma` atau `@prisma/client` dari Client Component / hook client.
- Pisahkan logic server (`lib/.../fetch*.ts` + API route) vs shared types (`*-types.ts`).
- Validasi input API dengan **zod**; auth via `getSessionFromRequest`.
